{"tid":2207634,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(說好的大國勃起呢？) 俄售軍武給印度中網友氣炸 中官媒反幫俄緩頰、怒斥小粉紅","createTime":"2020-09-18T09:50:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T17:20:19.000Z","uid":352783,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"20cb6307d5e1129334caf74010b93ff1523fa4b7","tid":2207634,"uid":352783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:50:09.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕中印邊境衝突日漸升溫，自6月中兩國軍隊在加勒萬河谷爆發武力衝突，雙方至今仍僵持不下，衝突一觸即發。而在此期間，俄羅斯仍繼續向印度出售新式戰機，並同意提前交付S-400遠程防空導彈系統，中國網友怒嗆俄國「捅刀中國」。不過，中國官媒《環球時報》卻幫俄國緩頰，稱印度買武器對俄軍工發展「意義重大」，更大罵批評俄國的人是「存心煽動」、製造敵意。<br />\n<br />\n綜合媒體，印度為中印衝突向俄國購買大量軍武，在印度外長出席6月24日的莫斯科閱兵時，還催促俄國提前交付一批S400防空飛彈。俄羅斯不但同意，還向印度出售了1千輛坦克和33架戰機，並以非常低的價格出售大量AL-41引擎給印度，這是俄國授權印度生產100多架Su-35戰機的一部分，合約還允許印度利用Su-35技術，升級Su-30機隊，將武器技術轉移給印度。<br />\n<br />\n中國網友對俄國如此友好印度，怒指責俄羅斯在幫印度捅刀中國。不過，16日才因美國政府將軍售台灣多達7種主要武器系統而崩潰發社論怒嗆的《環球時報》卻幫俄羅斯緩頰，總編胡錫進15日撰寫評論文章護航，稱印度是俄羅斯武器的長期最大買家之一，向印度賣武器對俄軍工發展意義重大，說中俄在保持所謂「新時代全面戰略協作夥伴關係的同時，也有各自「多元的外交利益」，並指在中印衝突中，俄羅斯扮演調停角色。<br />\n<br />\n此外，他將砲火指向自家人，怒斥批評俄羅斯的中國網友「是存心想要煽動，要在中俄兩國之間製造敵意」，還說中俄之間「結伴不結盟」，因為彼此不是盟友，所以「要求俄羅斯在中印衝突中選邊中國，是做不到的，也是不公平的」。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3295623?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3295623%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&d=U3in%2BbByR8w%2FZmejrHnAdYCLuBk19a2msHWYQfvuVO4%3D&h=d15a5fc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3295623%3Futm_medium%3DAPP%26utm_campaign%3DSHARE%26utm_medium%3DAPP&h=5c437652\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3295623?utm_medium=APP&amp;utm_campaign=SHARE&amp;utm_medium=APP</a><br />\n<br />\n支共果然係黃俄孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔敢罵Daddy<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1465fafc47ec6d8d515308da3c44d44c55743a83","tid":2207634,"uid":13343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T09:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9115bf0bff6334e5797c9e75d595450adf9440f","tid":2207634,"uid":245347,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"如果鬧左俄佬<br />\n一但開波<br />\n就真係無人幫支國了"},{"pid":"2e956209b97344ee95d8d18f306380af1b614095","tid":2207634,"uid":313615,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯銷售拳套"},{"pid":"d78b36f4d799f7a8fcb824a9702a8e79dbd994fa","tid":2207634,"uid":123970,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"e9115bf0bff6334e5797c9e75d595450adf9440f","tid":2207634,"uid":245347,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:07:34.000Z","msg":"如果鬧左俄佬<br />\n一但開波<br />\n就真係無人幫支國了"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:23:03.000Z","msg":"鬧唔鬧蛾佬都唔會幫, 唔喺背後桶一刀已經偷笑啦。"},{"pid":"260230b61e520eadd41dccb890105c9cc99e19de","tid":2207634,"uid":119232,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:28:10.000Z","msg":"欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d298641565739e2de72916d95e98274e5d5eea36","tid":2207634,"uid":32667,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:31:39.000Z","msg":"網友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，咩胡錫進呢，重唔出黎吠兩聲嘅,唔夠膽？"},{"pid":"13d231daa7eeb90fe94bfc008be36e8104f6dd17","tid":2207634,"uid":115579,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T10:34:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />台<br />\n<br /